<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="statement-n">statement <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'steɪtmənt/    美 /'steɪtmənt/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>声明；陈述：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>public</strong> / written / <strong>an official statement</strong>
公开/书面/正式声明</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A government spokesperson <strong>made / issued a statement</strong> to the press.
政府发言人向新闻界发表了一份声明。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The detective <strong>took a statement</strong> from both witnesses.
警探把两个证人的陈述都记录了下来。</p></div></div>